ke":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7c3c5c920b54808bc3c4895f3ce4513fb309e593","tid":897552,"uid":92178,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"4a72c1dd7ba43524132cf74253d9f9b3168d2ffb","tid":897552,"uid":173002,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T14:17:51.000Z","msg":"中共當然要淡化哩件世界大事，<br />\n中國抗日戰爭，係中華民國發動叛亂嘅共產黨，宜家將抗日功勞據我既有，<br />\n一次大戰，中國共產黨根本未出世，無得話自己有功勞，無辦法扭曲歷史，詎就宣揚今日係購物節，將全世界都紀念嘅歷史大事淡化，反正中國同世界嘅價值觀都唔接軌。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T14:21:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T14:28:26.000Z","msg":"今日係一次大戰結束一百週年，下個月至係英國香港被日本吞併紀念日，今年嘅香港重光(重歸英國)紀念日已經過左要等下年"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T14:36:54.000Z","msg":"唔止係一戰結束，亦都係和平紀念日"},{"pid":"e4fea8279ef746144743db5a1c30785a7cab91b8","tid":897552,"uid":92178,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T14:41:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cc1d6bb8374fa782f6ec05c32d5031d48d283cb9","tid":897552,"uid":61882,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T15:02:53.000Z","msg":"一則舊/趣聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中英一場外交風波<br />\n11月11日是英國的&ldquo;Remembrance Day&rdquo;，陣亡對陣亡將士的敬重和追思，英國很多的官員及民眾會佩戴Poppy。因此，這一天又稱&ldquo;Poppy Day&rdquo;。因文化語境，歷史認知的不同，曾引發了中英之間一場外交風波。<br />\n2010年11月，英國首相卡梅倫率團訪問中國時，正值英國&ldquo;陣亡將士紀念日&rdquo;前夕，英方訪華團成員每人都在胸前衣襟上佩帶了一小朵鮮紅的罌粟。罌粟被中國方面認知為罌粟花。在中國，罌粟花往往被聯想到鴉片戰爭。<span style=\"color: red;\">卡梅倫等訪華團成員在北京人民大會堂裡，拒絕了中方提出的摘除罌粟的要求。</span>一名首相府人員說：&ldquo;中方人員說我們佩戴罌粟花是不恰當的，因為兩國曾經發生鴉片戰爭我們告訴他們這花對我們有重大意義，我們所有人會繼續佩戴。&rdquo;<br />\n英文的虞美人花（虞美人）與罌粟花（鴉片罌粟）雖然有相同的簡稱（poppy），但&ldquo;poppy&rdquo;直譯過來就是&ldquo;罌粟花&rdquo;。<span style=\"color: red;\">許多中方人士認為英方成員佩戴的是&ldquo;罌粟花&ldquo;外交禮節是以主方（非客方）的文化背景，歷史習俗為主因此，英方的傲慢，自大與失禮引發了中國公眾的反感</span>。&rdquo;泰晤士報&ldquo;報導說：卡梅倫的罌粟花&ldquo;勾起東道主的不愉快回憶&rdquo;。"},{"pid":"2c4cecb404b8ecb7eed17d6aab592462d120452d","tid":897552,"uid":57677,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T16:50:31.000Z","msg":"如果係真花算唔算藏毒？"},{"pid":"61e7f8602d0262287e7a0e5cd4d6c7f17cba4eef","tid":897552,"uid":196099,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"2c4cecb404b8ecb7eed17d6aab592462d120452d","tid":897552,"uid":57677,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T16:50:31.000Z","msg":"如果係真花算唔算藏毒？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T16:51:25.000Z","msg":"你都真係冇改錯名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7412e4243862060b5dfc6f21e32b190bf2195ef8","tid":897552,"uid":52132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T16:57:11.000Z","msg":"M&amp;S 搵唔到 <br />\n聽日仲有咩地方有？"},{"pid":"11ffb6585db5fa43971c3489a1647b4277c30229","tid":897552,"uid":41035,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T23:07:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nV3CMqp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnV3CMqp.jpg&h=b746d7d1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"35f6240954a799d627810a28fa3a67d5e57d2057","tid":897552,"uid":196099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"11ffb6585db5fa43971c3489a1647b4277c30229","tid":897552,"uid":41035,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T23:07:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nV3CMqp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnV3CMqp.jpg&h=b746d7d1&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T01:13:44.000Z","msg":"Badges Story 度買？"},{"pid":"7dada10f019285376881c58fb0be9e8efe20544e","tid":897552,"uid":41035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"35f6240954a799d627810a28fa3a67d5e57d2057","tid":897552,"uid":196099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"11ffb6585db5fa43971c3489a1647b4277c30229","tid":897552,"uid":41035,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T23:07:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nV3CMqp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnV3CMqp.jpg&h=b746